    "name": "Luma Dream Machine API",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json",
    "description": {
      "content": "REST API for Luma's Dream Machine generative video and image platform.\nSubmit a generation request, then poll for its status by ID. Resources\ninclude video generations (Ray models), image generations (Photon),\nupscale, modify (style transfer), reframe, audio attachment, credits,\nand concepts.\nAuthentication uses Bearer tokens obtained from\nhttps://lumalabs.ai/dream-machine/api/keys.\n\n\nContact Support:\n Name: Luma Labs",
      "type": "text/plain"
    }
  }
